A new article on <b>Caltech News</b> titled <a href="https://www.caltech.edu/about/news/quantum-entanglement-of-photons-doubles-microscope-resolution">"Quantum Entanglement of Photons Doubles Microscope Resolution"</a> covers our recent progress in quantum imaging.

The original paper is published on <i>Nature Communications</i> and can be accessed <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-023-38191-4">here</a>.
